name: 303 Complete Skateboard
description:
Completes are now available from the online store!!! Completes come with Thunder or Independent Trucks, 303/CLFX/Street Trash Wheels, and Abec 7 Bearings! You save $30, plus FREE SHIPPING!


Please select a size option below. You can choose from any available 303, CLFX, or Street Trash decks and wheels.

Board and wheel graphics change monthly.
Please call 303-860-1303 (Local) or 1-877-303-2303 to check availability on deck and wheels or if you have any questions.
